{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Simple A/B tool for REAPER. Compare your mix with a reference track, match levels, and solo frequency bands to check your balance. Requires 4 channels on the Master Track (1/2 Mix, 3/4 Reference).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Donations: https://ko-fi.com/thelittlecavern\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sets the volume of all receives on selected tracks to -inf dB. Includes undo support.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sets the volume of all receives on all tracks in the project to -inf dB.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sets all sends on selected tracks to 0 dB.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
